<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_Redirector is used for all about HTTP redirection ( aka Location header and 30x codes)
However, the HTTP protocol defines a header that can be used to delay the Refreshness of a client. Here is a simple PHP example :</p>

<p>header('Refresh: 3; url= <a href="http://www.mysite.com/mypage/">http://www.mysite.com/mypage/</a> ');</p>

<p>Redirector should be given a way to use that.</p>

